{"tid":1256282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李飛：為何每次反政府示威都有暴力事件","createTime":"2019-06-25T02:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T05:09:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":356,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"676ccf3a373fed4136998b4bea7c63aad42425f2","tid":1256282,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1464842_1_20190625100208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1464842_1_20190625100208.jpg&h=1f60a365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大憲法和法律委員會主任委員李飛表示，不清楚香港修訂逃犯條例的事宜，但批評香港早前在反修例期間，示威者對警察採取傷害的方法，反問為甚麼每次反對政府都有暴力事件。<br />\n<br />\n李飛形容，對前陣子在香港的情況不可理解，認為香港是個法治地方，可以和平集會遊行，表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n被問到事件是否反映香港人對內地司法的信心不足，他表示不要說別的事，不管如何擔心也不能違法。<br />\n<br />\n出席人大常委會的基本法委員會主任沈春耀，沒有回應香港因修例引起的大遊行和示威。"},{"pid":"9a5e8d06d68a3c44b22cce5a8ebc8e1f8d13f7cc","tid":1256282,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464842-20190625.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464842-20190625.htm&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443sTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=e0ccf235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464842-20190625.htm&h=2e6b7650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464842-20190625.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2a375a5923d3d3eacaf2425c8a2bf68afc8986a3","tid":1256282,"uid":191453,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKRASFu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKRASFu.pn